{"tid":1594901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大紅底網民Toby Gu話香港人係狗","createTime":"2019-09-25T19:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T09:32:56.000Z","uid":172141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78c8cde57fc6dde15e9f458868f3c397409614f4","tid":1594901,"uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:37:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搵人搞搞佢好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢啲instagram鍾意de人comment就炸佢老母 @guutoby</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢條仆街拍完沙田事件，俾人話之後就開始玩野</span></span></strong><br />\n簡單概括啦，呢條友IG大概萬幾人follow既，就黎香港拍片搏like刷存在感，但係大把人都係咁啦，咁點解佢俾人屌呢？（姓氏係一件事）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 整假記者證</span></strong>：vlog影自己印假證，之後被屌仲係自己FB post話記者協會係on9佢自己開個都得冇問題，但係CBC聯絡佢就話佢既證件係真既<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 清楚講想人打交</span></strong>：（幾個vlog都有咁講）；根據CBC既描述，顧先生既vlog話自己個trip係<strong>pretty exciting stuff, 同埋想&quot;bad things to happen&quot;，想見到人打交等自己有爆野拍出黎</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. post一條&quot;raw footage&quot;</span></strong>：raw footage唔係問題，但係冇交代前因後果同埋video中間有唔少煽動既reporting，而俾人屌佢係冇悔意<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 佢話我地屌佢好似狗追波咁</span></strong>：簡單啲黎講姐係佢話我地屌佢冇道理，所以佢繼續post繼續troll<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5. IG story不斷挑機</span></strong>：覺得自己冇問題不特止，de屌佢既comment都不特止，佢既ig story話人send death threats但係全部剩係話fuck you（佢聲稱有人話會&quot;slit his throat&quot;），仲拍片掉自己頂頭盔話本身想捐物資但而家唔會（信你一成都多）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁大家就自行判斷啦，我唔support online bullying<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，學顧先生講：I'm just reporting facts</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">Source: <br />\n第一條 link 係 HKFP Richard Scotford<br />\n第二條係加拿大CBC News<br />\n第三條佢本人個地球post（已關comment）<br />\n第四條係佢個ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">P. S. 多謝加拿大媒體support香港人對呢啲仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2028183263949646?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARDNWfeRSnRv9977FumsqK9HGidNcgwvkJxygUdBP5KrRrSRj4a11-C4aoJUViQNJuyQ9pMwMIgQSDBjlLJdqzwfnQeRNr06yFBAOJtzyAEfukMqpzK0Eynwog3M1xhy-clo0m7lXOXB5RVIh423CCD0yJisKuUD_HEZuksnE4Uoap-UycvsH6p_fZnXX5bQwAbcdFYvdqFmwooGuhCMUZonmj8Dqqd71AkHzuSX9g8FeZ5THAndF9Mqqy0cwo3pxS0T6X6Qg-fJVDwFusaUncuMuxQDUCr4CpVmXsaT2-awI-cm-qwn1xkkOygEGXaJUPfqk7x0NgHEyCn4XszFW35IKw&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2Fposts%2F2028183263949646%3F__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARDNWfeRSnRv9977FumsqK9HGidNcgwvkJxygUdBP5KrRrSRj4a11-C4aoJUViQNJuyQ9pMwMIgQSDBjlLJdqzwfnQeRNr06yFBAOJtzyAEfukMqpzK0Eynwog3M1xhy-clo0m7lXOXB5RVIh423CCD0yJisKuUD_HEZuksnE4Uoap-UycvsH6p_fZnXX5bQwAbcdFYvdqFmwooGuhCMUZonmj8Dqqd71AkHzuSX9g8FeZ5THAndF9Mqqy0cwo3pxS0T6X6Qg-fJVDwFusaUncuMuxQDUCr4CpVmXsaT2-awI-cm-qwn1xkkOygEGXaJUPfqk7x0NgHEyCn4XszFW35IKw%26__tn__%3D-R&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=943a430b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2028183263949646?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARDNWfeRSnRv9977FumsqK9HGidNcgwvkJxygUdBP5KrRrSRj4a11-C4aoJUViQNJuyQ9pMwMIgQSDBjlLJdqzwfnQeRNr06yFBAOJtzyAEfukMqpzK0Eynwog3M1xhy-clo0m7lXOXB5RVIh423CCD0yJisKuUD_HEZuksnE4Uoap-UycvsH6p_fZnXX5bQwAbcdFYvdqFmwooGuhCMUZonmj8Dqqd71AkHzuSX9g8FeZ5THAndF9Mqqy0cwo3pxS0T6X6Qg-fJVDwFusaUncuMuxQDUCr4CpVmXsaT2-awI-cm-qwn1xkkOygEGXaJUPfqk7x0NgHEyCn4XszFW35IKw&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/to