地屌佢冇道理，所以佢繼續post繼續troll<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5. IG story不斷挑機</span></strong>：覺得自己冇問題不特止，de屌佢既comment都不特止，佢既ig story話人send death threats但係全部剩係話fuck you（佢聲稱有人話會&quot;slit his throat&quot;），仲拍片掉自己頂頭盔話本身想捐物資但而家唔會（信你一成都多）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁大家就自行判斷啦，我唔support online bullying<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，學顧先生講：I'm just reporting facts</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">Source: <br />\n第一條 link 係 HKFP Richard Scotford<br />\n第二條係加拿大CBC News<br />\n第三條佢本人個地球post（已關comment）<br />\n第四條係佢個ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">P. S. 多謝加拿大媒體support香港人對呢啲仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2028183263949646?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARDNWfeRSnRv9977FumsqK9HGidNcgwvkJxygUdBP5KrRrSRj4a11-C4aoJUViQNJuyQ9pMwMIgQSDBjlLJdqzwfnQeRNr06yFBAOJtzyAEfukMqpzK0Eynwog3M1xhy-clo0m7lXOXB5RVIh423CCD0yJisKuUD_HEZuksnE4Uoap-UycvsH6p_fZnXX5bQwAbcdFYvdqFmwooGuhCMUZonmj8Dqqd71AkHzuSX9g8FeZ5THAndF9Mqqy0cwo3pxS0T6X6Qg-fJVDwFusaUncuMuxQDUCr4CpVmXsaT2-awI-cm-qwn1xkkOygEGXaJUPfqk7x0NgHEyCn4XszFW35IKw&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2Fposts%2F2028183263949646%3F__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARDNWfeRSnRv9977FumsqK9HGidNcgwvkJxygUdBP5KrRrSRj4a11-C4aoJUViQNJuyQ9pMwMIgQSDBjlLJdqzwfnQeRNr06yFBAOJtzyAEfukMqpzK0Eynwog3M1xhy-clo0m7lXOXB5RVIh423CCD0yJisKuUD_HEZuksnE4Uoap-UycvsH6p_fZnXX5bQwAbcdFYvdqFmwooGuhCMUZonmj8Dqqd71AkHzuSX9g8FeZ5THAndF9Mqqy0cwo3pxS0T6X6Qg-fJVDwFusaUncuMuxQDUCr4CpVmXsaT2-awI-cm-qwn1xkkOygEGXaJUPfqk7x0NgHEyCn4XszFW35IKw%26__tn__%3D-R&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=943a430b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2028183263949646?__xts__%5B0%5D=6